{"id":"dcb1bf9a-0b43-4d80-a1e3-a6ef114af4a5","title":"1526/04","type":"main-list-block","children":[{"id":"4358d3e1-8b6b-4607-80d0-d10a959d148d","type":"standoff-editor-block","text":"From Florence, [April ..., 1526].","standoffProperties":[{"id":"0e644601-1114-416c-b1cf-df4b07eada7b","type":"codex/entity-reference","start":5,"end":12,"value":"671ee7e7-ae1b-4a5a-9591-b40203d5108f","zeroPoint":false,"metadata":[]},{"id":"487a5fa7-6400-4825-962e-d9c4147e70e3","type":"codex/time-reference","start":16,"end":30,"value":"95d1c274-6fbf-43a0-b6bc-95b4c2d63528","zeroPoint":false,"metadata":[]}],"blockProperties":[]},{"id":"2c10cf91-b179-4abf-8646-2b0b80e2016b","type":"standoff-editor-block","text":"To Messer Giovan Francesco Fattucci,","standoffProperties":[{"id":"24269806-86f7-4642-8f0e-844568398585","type":"style/italics","start":0,"end":34,"value":null,"zeroPoint":false,"metadata":[]},{"id":"3bb8a9d7-5de9-4031-a0f4-50f3d13a602a","type":"codex/entity-reference","start":3,"end":34,"value":"a4393234-2745-42ec-ba3e-42e4c52edb0c","zeroPoint":false,"metadata":[]}],"blockProperties":[]},{"id":"20d68ce7-9ce1-48e1-b8e6-286a88fe6476","type":"standoff-editor-block","text":"in Rome.","standoffProperties":[{"id":"6c9ee0fe-c67a-45c5-b7ad-54aab42511e1","type":"codex/entity-reference","start":3,"end":6,"value":"501a8a32-2c8a-4934-9060-8c7e36339f0f","zeroPoint":false,"metadata":[]}],"blockProperties":[]},{"id":"17d18232-c8e5-491a-9b5a-e0b4921ccea4","type":"standoff-editor-block","text":"","standoffProperties":[],"blockProperties":[]},{"id":"7ddf5cc8-2125-4038-b21c-0d29b74cec61","type":"standoff-editor-block","text":"Messere Giovan Francesco,\u00A0\u2014\u00A0During the coming week I shall have the figures already blocked out in the Sacristy covered up, because I want to leave the Sacristy free for the marble masons, whom I wish to build up the other tomb opposite the one already\u00A0erected. It is all squared work, or nearly so. I have\u00A0been thinking that the vault might be done while this work is in progress, for, given enough men, I think\u00A0that it could be finished in two or three\u00A0months,\u00A0though I do not know much about it. At the end of this coming week His Holiness might send Maestro Giovanni da Udine, if he should wish the work to be done now; I shall be quite ready for him.","standoffProperties":[{"id":"55c2fdf6-1af2-45e3-bf4f-af6f55c340fd","type":"codex/meta-relation-reference","start":0,"end":23,"value":"74305229-7612-4396-b8e7-ee02efe9eb54","zeroPoint":false,"metadata":[]},{"id":"26e29b92-dffd-486b-9d3b-238f4157a7c1","type":"style/uppercase","start":0,"end":23,"value":null,"zeroPoint":false,"metadata":[]},{"id":"e5bd7e6e-7ffb-4eba-a9fc-123442a38af1","type":"codex/entity-reference","start":0,"end":23,"value":"a4393234-2745-42ec-ba3e-42e4c52edb0c","zeroPoint":false,"metadata":[]},{"id":"b24ddf49-ba08-4f75-8756-cd6a18721083","type":"codex/entity-reference","start":51,"end":51,"value":"add92e01-cefe-4f13-94dd-f00eb82155b0","zeroPoint":false,"metadata":[]},{"id":"3e1b4226-7b98-4a5c-8c52-b9ecbf7aca8b","type":"codex/entity-reference","start":103,"end":110,"value":"845088ab-be6e-4ab5-b51a-7e85d09dff8a","zeroPoint":false,"metadata":[]},{"id":"74b0ef7c-3f62-48e9-a19e-c3bdb4a65a9b","type":"codex/entity-reference","start":132,"end":132,"value":"add92e01-cefe-4f13-94dd-f00eb82155b0","zeroPoint":false,"metadata":[]},{"id":"5db3ca3e-5622-4cc1-a6ab-27245076a452","type":"codex/entity-reference","start":152,"end":159,"value":"845088ab-be6e-4ab5-b51a-7e85d09dff8a","zeroPoint":false,"metadata":[]},{"id":"1897deaf-34fb-46fb-a169-6ef121a2704b","type":"codex/entity-reference","start":194,"end":194,"value":"add92e01-cefe-4f13-94dd-f00eb82155b0","zeroPoint":false,"metadata":[]},{"id":"ba75b095-06ce-48e9-a2f6-f7280809eba2","type":"codex/entity-reference","start":300,"end":300,"value":"add92e01-cefe-4f13-94dd-f00eb82155b0","zeroPoint":false,"metadata":[]},{"id":"e682ba47-cc8f-40d2-91cc-3bdf76ce39e8","type":"codex/entity-reference","start":405,"end":405,"value":"add92e01-cefe-4f13-94dd-f00eb82155b0","zeroPoint":false,"metadata":[]},{"id":"9b823391-f19c-445a-a94c-07377a4bb314","type":"codex/entity-reference","start":470,"end":470,"value":"add92e01-cefe-4f13-94dd-f00eb82155b0","zeroPoint":false,"metadata":[]},{"id":"8bf1a604-d0ed-492e-91a4-85a55e528f2d","type":"codex/entity-reference","start":530,"end":541,"value":"56a66a9e-ca50-45be-b8aa-aef2d47b5d96","zeroPoint":false,"metadata":[]},{"id":"6ac5a19b-fd44-4203-88c6-3cdd62bcf432","type":"codex/entity-reference","start":562,"end":578,"value":"07dd4e03-000d-4e8b-804e-797659a830ac","zeroPoint":false,"metadata":[]},{"id":"8792afe6-4599-436a-9b38-65c652035b20","type":"codex/entity-reference","start":584,"end":585,"value":"56a66a9e-ca50-45be-b8aa-aef2d47b5d96","zeroPoint":false,"metadata":[]},{"id":"1c9ca34e-ab10-4ff1-9172-ee9be518c59e","type":"codex/entity-reference","start":624,"end":624,"value":"add92e01-cefe-4f13-94dd-f00eb82155b0","zeroPoint":false,"metadata":[]},{"id":"a15dd0d0-ada1-4ef8-b568-ac1f57c7fa63","type":"codex/entity-reference","start":651,"end":653,"value":"07dd4e03-000d-4e8b-804e-797659a830ac","zeroPoint":false,"metadata":[]}],"blockProperties":[]},{"id":"9c137e01-0677-4d4c-9224-b030f5061226","type":"standoff-editor-block","text":"","standoffProperties":[],"blockProperties":[]},{"id":"3b8ee3a1-9008-4fe0-93b3-66357270ef61","type":"standoff-editor-block","text":"During this week four of the columns in the recess have been put up, while another was already in position. The niches are not so well forward: however, I think it will be entirely finished in four months\u0027 time. The ceiling could be begun at once, but the\u00A0lime-wood for it is not yet in the proper condition. We shall do our best to let it be as well seasoned as\u00A0possible.","standoffProperties":[{"id":"4b059c12-92d3-4760-b456-b461ceda2083","type":"codex/entity-reference","start":153,"end":153,"value":"add92e01-cefe-4f13-94dd-f00eb82155b0","zeroPoint":false,"metadata":[]}],"blockProperties":[]},{"id":"950c6c44-dcf4-4b93-a3ee-1d81a0c97ba7","type":"standoff-editor-block","text":"","standoffProperties":[],"blockProperties":[]},{"id":"07b9d4ff-94b6-4a3f-9e80-f92723690464","type":"standoff-editor-block","text":"I am working as fast as I can, and within a fortnight I shall begin work upon the other Captain;\u00A0after that the only important works remaining to be done will be the four Rivers. The four figures on the sarcophagi, the four figures on the ground\u00A0\u2014\u00A0which are the Rivers\u00A0\u2014\u00A0the two Captains, and the Madonna which is to be placed over the tomb at the head of the sacristy\u00A0\u2014\u00A0these are the figures I should like to carve myself. Six of them are already begun and I am confident that I can finish them in due time, and\u00A0a part of the others also, which are less important. There is nothing more to tell: commend me to Giovanni Spina and beg him to write to Figiovanni:\u00A0beg him also not to take away\u00A0the carters and send them to Pescia, because we should be left without stone. More than this, ask him not to make the stone-cutters\u00A0discontented by saying to them in a kindly way:\u00A0\u0022These people seem to have but little mercy on you, to make you work until the evening in these\u00A0days when\u00A0it is dark at the second hour.\u0022","standoffProperties":[{"id":"c40a0d90-0d28-49af-b5a9-8f9ec28fa94e","type":"codex/entity-reference","start":0,"end":0,"value":"add92e01-cefe-4f13-94dd-f00eb82155b0","zeroPoint":false,"metadata":[]},{"id":"f4cd8cd0-96ae-499f-b867-64d9442be5cd","type":"codex/entity-reference","start":24,"end":24,"value":"add92e01-cefe-4f13-94dd-f00eb82155b0","zeroPoint":false,"metadata":[]},{"id":"2f2cec1b-2b91-4164-93f9-228fa1554bb2","type":"codex/entity-reference","start":54,"end":54,"value":"add92e01-cefe-4f13-94dd-f00eb82155b0","zeroPoint":false,"metadata":[]},{"id":"783c3444-0bb0-4482-b608-62fdaeaeb336","type":"codex/document-reference","start":96,"end":96,"value":"719f9fae-2f56-4c5d-a995-9efacf9fea3b","zeroPoint":true,"metadata":[]},{"id":"d039293c-a7ef-43b2-9ea3-b6a8dcc47083","type":"codex/entity-reference","start":360,"end":367,"value":"845088ab-be6e-4ab5-b51a-7e85d09dff8a","zeroPoint":false,"metadata":[]},{"id":"54bdba9c-8e82-48cc-b443-8ebd7875f497","type":"codex/entity-reference","start":393,"end":393,"value":"add92e01-cefe-4f13-94dd-f00eb82155b0","zeroPoint":false,"metadata":[]},{"id":"de47447f-ee99-4512-b584-39ed3a404802","type":"codex/entity-reference","start":416,"end":421,"value":"add92e01-cefe-4f13-94dd-f00eb82155b0","zeroPoint":false,"metadata":[]},{"id":"83808b24-a795-40f8-881b-70ce8ad00bc2","type":"codex/entity-reference","start":458,"end":458,"value":"add92e01-cefe-4f13-94dd-f00eb82155b0","zeroPoint":false,"metadata":[]},{"id":"f5b793fc-6bdd-4709-bc5b-571134066f50","type":"codex/entity-reference","start":478,"end":478,"value":"add92e01-cefe-4f13-94dd-f00eb82155b0","zeroPoint":false,"metadata":[]},{"id":"95c8e3bb-0bae-4115-8121-0ae8b154810c","type":"codex/entity-reference","start":605,"end":606,"value":"add92e01-cefe-4f13-94dd-f00eb82155b0","zeroPoint":false,"metadata":[]},{"id":"d7900550-47b0-49e5-99b1-a4c234710122","type":"codex/entity-reference","start":611,"end":624,"value":"1c7a5d40-9dea-41e9-b387-9c22d82d526f","zeroPoint":false,"metadata":[]},{"id":"8045a70c-6f42-4465-8036-d580c1c33944","type":"codex/entity-reference","start":634,"end":636,"value":"1c7a5d40-9dea-41e9-b387-9c22d82d526f","zeroPoint":false,"metadata":[]},{"id":"f23610b5-14e6-486c-b1fa-4288570b86be","type":"codex/entity-reference","start":650,"end":659,"value":"07fd9a1c-9416-4c99-b5c9-87c50efd32e4","zeroPoint":false,"metadata":[]},{"id":"c7a1a0d1-2a21-407d-ab34-752913cb5e7b","type":"codex/entity-reference","start":666,"end":668,"value":"1c7a5d40-9dea-41e9-b387-9c22d82d526f","zeroPoint":false,"metadata":[]},{"id":"b19d6196-69a2-41fa-b6e3-466ba4648c9d","type":"codex/entity-reference","start":721,"end":726,"value":"401131ae-2af1-4102-ae98-d7c619f5366e","zeroPoint":false,"metadata":[]},{"id":"b2d6752c-cc5e-4938-9473-1e436dc4dfb9","type":"codex/entity-reference","start":790,"end":792,"value":"1c7a5d40-9dea-41e9-b387-9c22d82d526f","zeroPoint":false,"metadata":[]},{"id":"99625d7e-a2ec-4c85-bc80-d4b062858fb7","type":"codex/entity-reference","start":810,"end":822,"value":"d0bc32c6-aacd-4c6b-9ef1-912f211a7b14","zeroPoint":false,"metadata":[]},{"id":"98d9fc81-df39-4b59-bd47-cf478d9209cb","type":"codex/entity-reference","start":850,"end":853,"value":"d0bc32c6-aacd-4c6b-9ef1-912f211a7b14","zeroPoint":false,"metadata":[]},{"id":"f642970c-e03e-4a6b-81a8-2b639c54c9b1","type":"codex/entity-reference","start":919,"end":921,"value":"d0bc32c6-aacd-4c6b-9ef1-912f211a7b14","zeroPoint":false,"metadata":[]},{"id":"89a29c17-cb30-4b79-a4bd-d6a86ae64702","type":"codex/entity-reference","start":932,"end":934,"value":"d0bc32c6-aacd-4c6b-9ef1-912f211a7b14","zeroPoint":false,"metadata":[]}],"blockProperties":[]},{"id":"ffb600d5-1fc9-4d56-b5c0-9d6c4af8e046","type":"standoff-editor-block","text":"","standoffProperties":[],"blockProperties":[]},{"id":"779fea3b-226c-43aa-a913-f16d78121fc6","type":"standoff-editor-block","text":"It requires a hundred eyes to keep any one man at his work, and even then your efforts may be spoilt by people who are too soft-hearted. Patience! I would to God that things which are not displeasing to Him were not displeasing to me!","standoffProperties":[{"id":"e75da6dc-e0e2-4a54-9b50-c56e110b5595","type":"codex/entity-reference","start":147,"end":147,"value":"add92e01-cefe-4f13-94dd-f00eb82155b0","zeroPoint":false,"metadata":[]},{"id":"f57d4ad4-21bd-49f5-b637-931764ebeead","type":"codex/entity-reference","start":158,"end":160,"value":"a3fed3ec-1814-4027-a2d5-ac598b2fcb6f","zeroPoint":false,"metadata":[]},{"id":"d2982aaf-fce9-4b75-8b5e-6a3967c7a8d4","type":"codex/entity-reference","start":203,"end":205,"value":"a3fed3ec-1814-4027-a2d5-ac598b2fcb6f","zeroPoint":false,"metadata":[]},{"id":"61970e4e-ac59-4977-9a3d-003ee1209bb2","type":"codex/entity-reference","start":231,"end":232,"value":"add92e01-cefe-4f13-94dd-f00eb82155b0","zeroPoint":false,"metadata":[]}],"blockProperties":[]}]}